Privacy Policy
--------------

Thank you for using Starcope! We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and share your information when you use our app.

Information We Collect

When you use our app, we may collect the following information:

Email address: We collect your email address when you sign up for our app. We use your email address to send you daily horoscope predictions and other updates related to our app.

Date of birth: We collect your date of birth when you sign up for our app. We use your date of birth to generate your daily horoscope predictions.

Device information: We may collect information about the device you use to access our app, such as your device's model, operating system, and IP address.

How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect from you to provide you with daily horoscope predictions and to improve our app. We may also use your information to personalize your experience on our app, such as by showing you content that is relevant to your interests.

Sharing Your Information

We will not sell or share your personal information with third parties for their own marketing purposes without your consent. We may share your information with third parties in the following circumstances:

With service providers: We may share your information with service providers who perform functions on our behalf, such as hosting our app or sending emails. These service providers are bound by confidentiality agreements and are not allowed to use your information for their own purposes.

As required by law: We may disclose your information if required to do so by law, such as in response to a subpoena or court order.

To protect our rights: We may disclose your information if we believe it is necessary to enforce our terms of service, protect our rights, or defend against legal claims.

Your Choices

You have the following choices regarding the information we collect from you:

Opting out of emails: You can opt out of receiving emails from us at any time by contacting us through the support email.

Deleting your account: You can delete your account at any time by contacting us through the support email. Please note that if you delete your account, your personal information will be permanently deleted and we will not be able to restore it.

Data Retention

We will retain your personal information for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide you with our services. If you delete your account, we will delete your personal information within a reasonable timeframe.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this privacy policy from time to time to reflect changes to our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We encourage you to review this privacy policy regularly for any changes.

Contact Us

If you have any questions about this privacy policy or our treatment of your personal information, please contact us at support@krayde.com
